item.title: Symmetree
item.description: I discovered a weird phenomena where if you look up at the sky through some bare branch trees, take a picture, and mirror it along the center - you can pretty much always find some sort of creepy religious figure. Like a bishop. I’ve never been religious but maybe this is that elusive generational trauma memory? lol
